Text: Janet is an outstanding senior engineer and consummate professional. She joined our team as a Senior Software Engineer. Thanks to her exceptional performance as a designer, developer, and mentor, she rose quickly to a technical leadership role in the company. I've never met anyone as broadly talented in software technology. But the icing on the cake is her ability to work with others. She's a naturally empathetic person, able to encourage and challenge those around her to learn and grow professionally and personally. She is an asset to any organization, and given the chance I'd hire her in a second.

Janet is deeply experienced and knowledgeable about all aspects of software engineering and design. She is also incredibly helpful and eager to teach what she knows to others.   I could give the usual platitudes about quality work, delivering on time, etc. Those are all true, but I can say those things about a lot of great people I've worked with. Yona goes far beyond that. She radiates a genuine positive attitude of cheerfulness and enthusiasm that lifts the spirits of everyone fortunate enough to work with her.

I had the great privilege of working with Ms. Jeffus at RealQuantum from 2022-2023.  She was the most experienced engineer on our team and as a result, was responsible for some of the most important and complex assignments, such as implementation of single sign-on (SSO) using Auth0 and Azure.  She was also extremely enthusiastic about helping others with any problem, doing flawless deployments, and leading our team meetings.  She would be a great asset to any team, including as lead developer or CTO, and I hope that I have the opportunity to work with her again in the future.

It has been a true privilege to work alongside Janet Jeffus at RealQuantum. As a Senior Software Engineer, her skill level is truly top-notch, and her ability to tackle even the most complex challenges is nothing short of impressive. Janet's expertise and deep understanding of software engineering have made her an indispensable asset to our team.  I have personally witnessed Janet's calm and confident approach when assisting colleagues facing difficult problems. Her willingness to lend a hand and provide guidance reflects her strong commitment to teamwork and collaboration. I had the opportunity to see her work on many complex projects and her contributions were invaluable to our successes.  Janet's advanced skillset, coupled with her extensive experience, make her an outstanding team player and a tremendous asset to any organization. I absolutely endorse Janet Jeffus as a Senior Software Engineer and am confident that she will continue to excel in any role she undertakes.

Yona was a valuable employee at Real Quantum, and I had the privilege to working with her and seeing her capabilities in action.  Her level of skill was top notch.  If I ever got stuck or ran into problems I was not able to resolve, she was quick to lend a hand with a confident and calm approach.  There was no task she was not capable of overcoming.  She was heavily involved with Single Sign-On using Auth0 and Azure, and I was able to work alongside her.    Yona's extensive experience in software engineering and advanced skillset to navigate the most difficult challenges makes her one of the most valuable team players any organization could ask for.

Janet knows more about programming then most software companies combined. She is excellent to work with, and I learned more in the 9 months I worked for her than the rest of my career combined. She would be an outstanding addition to, or leader of, any project.
